♪But our way does♪

59
00:03:08,050 --> 00:03:09,570
=Hidden Master=

60
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:13,540
=Episode 18=

61
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:17,600
Years ago, the Martial Artists
Association united all the major sects

62
00:03:17,870 --> 00:03:19,760
to eradicate the demonic sect.

63
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:22,470
It was believed
that once they were destroyed,

64
00:03:22,470 --> 00:03:24,040
the martial world would find peace.

65
00:03:24,470 --> 00:03:26,670
However, during the process,
they realized

66
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:29,480
that it was not the demonic sect
but human hearts

67
00:03:30,030 --> 00:03:31,440
that stirred up the chaos.

68
00:03:32,030 --> 00:03:33,190
Regardless of the demonic sect,

69
00:03:33,190 --> 00:03:34,310
Martial Artists Association,

70
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:35,960
and other sects in the martial world,

71
00:03:35,960 --> 00:03:37,390
the darkness within human hearts

72
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,480
was the hardest to eradicate.

73
00:03:40,520 --> 00:03:42,280
Wang Qing, tell them

74
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,790
I'm the love of your life!

75
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:44,870
They're so fierce!

76
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:46,080
That guy is Wang Qing.

77
00:03:46,430 --> 00:03:48,040
When fighting with the demonic sect,

78
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,790
he lost his right arm.

79
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,320
Normally, as a swordsman,

80
00:03:52,630 --> 00:03:54,040
he'd lead a miserable life.

81
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:56,960
However, he's running
a small business here

82
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,110
and living a happy life.

83
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,630
Is he really happy?

84
00:04:00,630 --> 00:04:01,790
Can't you tell?

85
00:04:02,170 --> 00:04:03,080
Hold on, Dad.

86
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,160
What did you just say?

87
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,790
He's a swordsman?

88
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,990
Well, he used to be.

89
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:10,360
Come on, Mr. Gou. Over here.

90
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:13,560
It's been ages since we met.

91
00:04:13,560 --> 00:04:14,920
I've missed you so much.

92
00:04:15,280 --> 00:04:16,390
Who would've thought

93
00:04:16,590 --> 00:04:18,230
Mr. Gui has such a story?

94
00:04:19,150 --> 00:04:21,030
However, from what I know
about Zhuge Yu,

95
00:04:21,030 --> 00:04:22,190
he wouldn't kill Ms. Shun

96
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:23,640
for the title of Sword Saint.

97
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:25,600
Mr. Gui,

98
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:28,310
your hardships are finally over.

99
00:04:28,310 --> 00:04:29,440
Your family is finally reunited.

100
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,480
Mr. Gui, Chairman Gou,

101
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,400
please enjoy.

102
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:42,910
Lingfeng's friend?

103
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,070
No, no, no.

104
00:04:44,070 --> 00:04:45,200
You're wrong.

105
00:04:45,360 --> 00:04:46,910
She's Heng's friend.

106
00:04:48,430 --> 00:04:50,750
Well, Mr. Gui, Chairman Gou,

107
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,600
please enjoy.

108
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:53,950
I'll leave you two alone.

109
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:58,640
Where's Yingdan?

110
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:01,640
She's Lingfeng's friend.

111
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:02,750
Okay, okay.

112
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:05,900
(Martial Artists Association)

113
00:05:06,870 --> 00:05:09,440
We live for justice!

114
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,590
You three are role models
of the association.

115
00:05:13,390 --> 00:05:15,440
You're all righteous and loyal.

116
00:05:16,430 --> 00:05:17,350
Gou Lingfeng,

117
00:05:18,070 --> 00:05:19,830
in the Puppet Knight's case,

118
00:05:19,830 --> 00:05:20,950
Vice Chairman's case,

119
00:05:20,950 --> 00:05:22,040
Prince Chang's case,

120
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,800
and Ye Dahei's case,

121
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:26,560
you've all done a good job.

122
00:05:27,870 --> 00:05:29,040
You've really defended

123
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,510
the dignity of the association

124
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,430
and prevented those with ill intentions

125
00:05:32,430 --> 00:05:33,710
from tarnishing our reputation.

126
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,910
Well done.

127
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,680
I'm doing all this to be

128
00:05:38,680 --> 00:05:40,950
a great hero like you.

129
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,160
Keep going.

130
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:46,350
Zhuge Heng.

131
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,040
You've done well too.

132
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:51,470
I heard you decided to carry on
your father's aspiration

133
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,710
and lead the Sword Alliance
in commercial development.

134
00:05:54,720 --> 00:05:56,000
I have high hopes for you.

135
00:05:56,360 --> 00:05:58,390
Chairman, you're wise and generous.

136
00:05:58,630 --> 00:05:59,590
From now on,

137
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,440
you are my idol too.

138
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:05,670
Floral Knight,

139
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,470
in Prince Chang's case,

140
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,390
you used your medical skills

141
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:12,350
to save many heroes and people.

142
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,710
Thank you so much.

143
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:17,390
This is all my duty.

144
00:06:17,630 --> 00:06:18,630
See?

145
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:19,480
I've told you

146
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,320
the chairman knows everything.

147
00:06:22,430 --> 00:06:23,880
You are our role models.

148
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:26,440
But remember, don't get carried away.

149
00:06:26,800 --> 00:06:28,560
Keep going forward.

150
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:30,000
Yes, Chairman!

151
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,640
Thank you, Chairman.

152
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,720
Have some tea.

153
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:44,920
Lingfeng,

154
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:48,080
do you remember what happened
when you were four?

155
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,470
Of course I do.

156
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:52,000
That year, the demonic sect
invaded my home

157
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,270
and killed my nanny.

158
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:55,030
If it weren't for you,

159
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,830
I would've died back then.

160
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,950
You still remember that?

161
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,470
Of course.

162
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,910
I've been keeping an eye on you.

163
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,270
Your father and I are old acquaintances.

164
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,950
The Gou Family Trade Association

165
00:07:09,500 --> 00:07:11,120
has been supporting us

166
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,710
in finance secretly.

167
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:13,830
So, it's true.

168
00:07:13,830 --> 00:07:15,510
I had some assumptions,

169
00:07:15,630 --> 00:07:17,470
but I didn't expect it to be true.

170
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:18,950
But Chairman...

171
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,270
Calling me Chairman feels distant.

172
00:07:21,510 --> 00:07:23,510
Your father and I
have been friends for years.

173
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:25,150
Why don't you call me

174
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:26,510
Uncle Wu?

175
00:07:27,740 --> 00:07:28,630
Uncle Wu,

176
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:30,640
why are you telling me all this?

177
00:07:32,630 --> 00:07:34,240
Zhu Gou Team's reputation

178
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,150
is rising in the martial world.

179
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,350
It has brought great honor to us.

180
00:07:39,630 --> 00:07:41,510
I'm truly proud of you.

181
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,560
However, as you know,

182
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:45,830
the demonic sect has been active lately.

183
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:47,680
You are born kind

184
00:07:47,830 --> 00:07:49,150
and trust others too easily.

185
00:07:50,190 --> 00:07:52,270
I'm worried that you'd be used
by bad people

186
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:53,590
and go astray.

187
00:07:54,160 --> 00:07:56,560
From now on, you must be

188
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,640
more careful.

189
00:07:59,390 --> 00:08:00,830
Thanks for your guidance, Uncle Wu.

190
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:04,240
I will not let you down.

191
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:08,190
Ling'er,

192
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,270
while I was away,

193
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:10,470
was everything alright at home?

194
00:08:12,070 --> 00:08:13,030
Nothing happened.

195
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:16,030
Heng, congratulations.

196
00:08:16,190 --> 00:08:17,150
They look so happy.

197
00:08:17,390 --> 00:08:18,310
Thank you.

198
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:19,950
Zhuge, congratulations.

199
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,830
You've fulfilled a lifelong wish.

200
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:23,310
- Come on, Yingdan.
- Come on.

201
00:08:23,310 --> 00:08:24,230
Thank you.

202
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,350
And of course, thank you, Ling'er.

203
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:31,640
That slap really woke me up.

204
00:08:32,120 --> 00:08:33,560
Heng, don't be too polite.

205
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:36,830
Zhuge, you don't need to pester me
about learning demonic skills.

206
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:38,430
Ling'er.

207
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:41,030
Zhuge has truly changed.

208
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:44,150
He's no longer the wandering kid
who's always

209
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:45,280
talking about revenge.

210
00:08:45,910 --> 00:08:47,510
Yes. Heng was really like

211
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:49,400
a troublesome kid.

212
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:51,480
Well,

213
00:08:51,480 --> 00:08:53,030
you don't need to learn demonic skills.

214
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,390
Instead, you can teach me sword skills.

215
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,400
I'll call you Master.

216
00:08:55,750 --> 00:08:56,830
Stop kidding.

217
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,280
You're still my master.

218
00:08:58,390 --> 00:09:00,520
I hope you can teach me business.

219
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:01,590
Business?

220
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,800
Why would you learn that?

221
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,160
My father was right.

222
00:09:04,510 --> 00:09:06,590
Conflicts in the martial world
are pointless.

223
00:09:06,750 --> 00:09:08,950
So, I've decided to quit martial arts

224
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:10,830
and start doing business.

225
00:09:11,750 --> 00:09:12,710
I'll expand

226
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:14,030
our business in Huizhou

227
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:16,280
for my father and the Sword Alliance.

228
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:18,510
That's great.

229
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:19,430
Therefore,

230
00:09:19,670 --> 00:09:21,470
my new three biggest wishes are

231
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,000
to strive,

232
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,120
to get rich,

233
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,000
and to build a family.

234
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:31,880
Ling'er,

235
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:33,350
maybe I spoke too soon.

236
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,400
I agree.

237
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:37,080
I understand why you want
to strive and get rich.

238
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,360
But build a family?

239
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,470
Who will be your wife?

240
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,320
Ling'er,

241
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:45,710
you can't let him get
what he wants easily.

242
00:09:46,030 --> 00:09:47,000
Master, what's the benefit of

243
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,200
giving me a hard time?

244
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,870
Besides, Ling'er

245
00:09:49,870 --> 00:09:51,470
has agreed.

246
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,830
- I can't believe it.
- Heng!

247
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,360
Yingdan,

248
00:09:54,630 --> 00:09:56,400
let's pick a date.

249
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:00,470
For them.

250
00:10:02,870 --> 00:10:04,150
Gou,

251
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:05,520
I haven't agreed!

252
00:10:05,670 --> 00:10:07,320
- You haven't?
- You did!

253
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,870
When we sat on the swing,

254
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:10,360
you said, "Heng, I agree!"

255
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,270
- You forgot it?
- Heng!

256
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:12,750
How can you back out?

257
00:10:12,750 --> 00:10:14,200
Ling'er hasn't said yes.

258
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:16,280
You're always bullying her.

259
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,000
Listen, Zhuge,

260
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,150
if you dare to bully her,

261
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:20,070
I'll...

262
00:10:20,440 --> 00:10:21,360
I wouldn't dare.

263
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:23,710
I've apologized to her.

264
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,160
But I really love her.

265
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:28,390
Zhuge Heng really loves her.

266
00:10:28,390 --> 00:10:30,520
After all, he told his father,

267
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,160
"She's a good girl,

268
00:10:32,270 --> 00:10:34,440
but it's too early to have a child."

269
00:10:34,440 --> 00:10:35,520
Master!

270
00:10:35,750 --> 00:10:36,670
Stop!

271
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,440
Heng,

272
00:10:38,440 --> 00:10:39,630
eat more.

273
00:10:39,630 --> 00:10:40,550
Okay.

274
00:10:43,390 --> 00:10:44,310
Master.

275
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,520
You two should also settle it quickly.

276
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:49,430
We?

277
00:10:49,550 --> 00:10:50,800
What do you mean?

278
00:10:52,870 --> 00:10:55,720
I... I'm going to be a great hero.

279
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:58,670
I still need to strive for Zhu Gou Team.

