is so ruthless!

565
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:41,920
Little Zhan, Yingdan,

566
00:23:41,920 --> 00:23:42,960
don't worry.

567
00:23:43,510 --> 00:23:45,400
My master asked me to go to Wulipo

568
00:23:45,400 --> 00:23:47,320
to attend the succession ceremony.

569
00:23:47,750 --> 00:23:49,830
We can use this chance
to uncover the truth

570
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,780
(Little Zhao's Grave)
for Little Zhao.

571
00:23:54,240 --> 00:23:56,310
What happened?

572
00:23:56,310 --> 00:23:57,270
We must find them.

573
00:23:57,270 --> 00:23:58,190
That's right.

574
00:24:03,160 --> 00:24:04,150
It's them again.

575
00:24:06,310 --> 00:24:07,230
Stop!

576
00:24:07,720 --> 00:24:08,760
Demonic sect member?

577
00:24:09,070 --> 00:24:10,830
Why are you here, boss?

578
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:12,000
We're just minions.

579
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:13,870
Why can't you spare us?

580
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:17,000
That young man is pretty.

581
00:24:18,440 --> 00:24:20,000
That one too.

582
00:24:22,350 --> 00:24:23,270
Look at me.

583
00:24:24,070 --> 00:24:25,800
Am I pretty?

584
00:24:28,110 --> 00:24:29,910
Don't be rude to our boss's friends.

585
00:24:32,680 --> 00:24:33,640
How did you get

586
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:35,150
the bruises?

587
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:38,430
We got beaten by the heroes
from the Martial Artists Association.

588
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:41,390
Is it that hard

589
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:42,790
for you to make a living?

590
00:24:42,790 --> 00:24:43,750
Yes, boss.

591
00:24:43,750 --> 00:24:46,040
We're planning to turn over a new leaf
and go home.

592
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,400
Boss.

593
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:50,240
No wonder you're the boss.

594
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:52,390
After being beaten,
you still ran so fast.

595
00:24:52,580 --> 00:24:53,440
What?

596
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:54,400
Boss, we were about

597
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:56,440
to join you, but you said
you were going home.

598
00:24:56,440 --> 00:24:58,680
Your line of work is so popular now.

599
00:24:58,680 --> 00:24:59,910
You're even recruiting new members.

600
00:25:00,380 --> 00:25:01,270
Boss,

601
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:03,680
I used to sing at the Newbud Teahouse

602
00:25:03,680 --> 00:25:06,280
beside the storytellers.

603
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:08,680
Later, they said my rhymes were terrible

604
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,040
and fired me.

605
00:25:10,440 --> 00:25:12,110
I had no choice but to do this.

606
00:25:12,110 --> 00:25:13,560
I think your rhymes are pretty good.

607
00:25:13,560 --> 00:25:14,440
Boss,

608
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:16,920
I used to be a host
at the Huizhou Drill Ground,

609
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:18,630
but they said I was too bad at writing

610
00:25:18,960 --> 00:25:20,200
and I couldn't

611
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,590
describe their heroic spirit.

612
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:24,240
I... I had no choice either.

613
00:25:24,590 --> 00:25:25,640
Boss, look.

614
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,680
We're all decent folks.

615
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:28,760
We're planning to go home and farm.

616
00:25:29,270 --> 00:25:30,160
Farm, yes, farm.

617
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,110
Go home and farm.

618
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,910
Look at you.

619
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:35,040
A bunch of villains.

620
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:37,720
They caught you robbing again, right?

621
00:25:38,050 --> 00:25:39,430
You did this to yourself!

622
00:25:39,960 --> 00:25:41,070
We had no choice, boss.

623
00:25:41,070 --> 00:25:42,270
We didn't succeed once this month.

624
00:25:42,270 --> 00:25:43,120
We're starving.

625
00:25:43,130 --> 00:25:44,390
We can't afford the dues.

626
00:25:44,550 --> 00:25:45,470
Dues?

627
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:52,280
Does the association charge you dues?

628
00:25:56,110 --> 00:25:57,560
Rascals!

629
00:25:58,070 --> 00:25:59,040
Let's go, Master.

630
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:00,630
We'll catch them.

631
00:26:03,640 --> 00:26:04,960
- Where are they?
- Over there.

632
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:05,880
Over there.

633
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:07,360
Let's go.

634
00:26:11,960 --> 00:26:14,350
Show some respect to the boss
from the demonic sect.

635
00:26:14,350 --> 00:26:15,960
I heard he's a ruthless killer.

636
00:26:16,310 --> 00:26:17,240
How's that possible?

637
00:26:17,350 --> 00:26:19,040
He seems pretty kind.

638
00:26:19,240 --> 00:26:20,430
I agree.

639
00:26:20,830 --> 00:26:22,110
He grows on people.

640
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:24,400
Boss, I feel like I've seen him

641
00:26:24,400 --> 00:26:26,390
somewhere else before.

642
00:26:28,070 --> 00:26:29,150
It's hard to be a leader.

643
00:26:29,270 --> 00:26:30,800
Don't overthink it. Let's go.

644
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:37,680
I told you that old man had money.

645
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:38,600
Stop.

646
00:26:39,550 --> 00:26:40,550
Who are you?

647
00:26:40,550 --> 00:26:42,030
Get lost.

648
00:26:42,030 --> 00:26:43,910
You're blocking my way!

649
00:26:48,720 --> 00:26:50,680
A defender of justice!

650
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,520
You're asking for this. Don't blame us.

651
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,390
Don't hit my face.

652
00:27:06,750 --> 00:27:07,750
You asked for this.

653
00:27:07,750 --> 00:27:09,240
You busybody!

654
00:27:10,920 --> 00:27:12,000
Go to hell!

655
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:19,390
Why is it him?

656
00:27:19,640 --> 00:27:20,630
Who's this?

657
00:27:21,350 --> 00:27:23,030
A demonic sect member I saved before.

658
00:27:23,030 --> 00:27:23,950
Hu San'er.

659
00:27:24,270 --> 00:27:25,190
Hu San'er?

660
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:26,920
I'll help him.

661
00:27:36,350 --> 00:27:37,880
- Stop!
- San'er!

662
00:27:37,880 --> 00:27:38,800
San'er!

663
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:40,790
- Mr. Zhuge!
- Get up.

664
00:27:40,790 --> 00:27:42,110
Mr. Zhuge!

665
00:27:44,270 --> 00:27:45,190
Let's go!

666
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:47,800
Are you alright?

667
00:27:48,590 --> 00:27:50,350
Mr. Zhuge!

668
00:27:50,350 --> 00:27:51,670
Alright, let's go.

669
00:27:55,590 --> 00:27:58,240
All the members of the Martial Artists
Association are bad people!

670
00:27:58,240 --> 00:28:00,040
They're always bullying us!

671
00:28:00,040 --> 00:28:01,240
Look what they did to me!

672
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,590
Alright, calm down.

673
00:28:02,590 --> 00:28:03,510
It's okay.

674
00:28:04,590 --> 00:28:05,720
Watch your words.

675
00:28:05,830 --> 00:28:07,430
You little demonic sect member,

676
00:28:07,550 --> 00:28:09,390
don't slander all heroes.

677
00:28:10,030 --> 00:28:11,390
Who are you?

678
00:28:12,550 --> 00:28:15,240
It seems like you're one of us.

679
00:28:15,550 --> 00:28:18,110
Who are these two?

680
00:28:18,110 --> 00:28:19,150
This is my master.

681
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:20,630
This is Yingdan.

682
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:22,390
This is Ms. Ling'er.

683
00:28:25,680 --> 00:28:26,720
Hello.

684
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,240
Hell no!

685
00:28:30,440 --> 00:28:32,030
All heroes are bad people

686
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:33,040
except for Mr. Zhuge!

687
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,080
You...

688
00:28:34,880 --> 00:28:37,560
Don't be blinded by a few rascals!

689
00:28:37,830 --> 00:28:38,800
Is that so?

690
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:41,270
The association has ruled
the martial world for years.

691
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:42,520
Has the world found peace?

692
00:28:42,790 --> 00:28:44,720
Bandits still roam freely,

693
00:28:44,720 --> 00:28:46,280
and many commoners are homeless.

694
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:48,000
As you can see,

695
00:28:48,000 --> 00:28:49,350
they even colluded with those villains

696
00:28:49,350 --> 00:28:50,630
to collect protection fees.

697
00:28:52,070 --> 00:28:53,040
Listen,

698
00:28:53,310 --> 00:28:54,560
a true hero

699
00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:57,640
would never demean themselves to join
the Martial Artists Association,

700
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,820
an organization rotten inside!

701
00:28:59,820 --> 00:29:00,910
Okay, fine.

702
00:29:01,070 --> 00:29:02,040
Then tell me,

703
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:04,320
where can we find a true hero?

704
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,520
I'm a true hero!

705
00:29:08,510 --> 00:29:09,550
Well, well.

706
00:29:09,780 --> 00:29:11,040
That's enough.

707
00:29:11,460 --> 00:29:13,540
Stop bragging.
You're making me confused.

708
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:16,240
- I...
- Here, San'er.

709
00:29:16,240 --> 00:29:17,520
Take the money

710
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:18,600
and go home.

711
00:29:21,240 --> 00:29:22,520
Mr. Zhuge,

712
00:29:23,030 --> 00:29:25,240
you're always so kind to me.

713
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:28,160
The divine sect will never
forget your generosity.

714
00:29:28,160 --> 00:29:29,840
Alright, just go home.

715
00:29:32,750 --> 00:29:33,670
San'er,

716
00:29:34,030 --> 00:29:35,110
let me ask you something.

717
00:29:35,400 --> 00:29:37,280
Do you know where Wulipo is?

718
00:29:37,790 --> 00:29:39,040
Of course.

719
00:29:39,440 --> 00:29:40,750
My home is there.

720
00:29:40,750 --> 00:29:42,800
Well, lead the way!

721
00:29:44,790 --> 00:29:45,710
Let's go.

722
00:29:45,900 --> 00:29:51,420
(Peace and Harvest)

723
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:54,480
- We're here.
- Make way, please.

724
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:55,400
This...

725
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,430
Don't lose it.

726
00:30:02,510 --> 00:30:03,430
Do you mean

727
00:30:03,920 --> 00:30:05,520
they're all demonic sect members?

728
00:30:05,720 --> 00:30:06,800
Including this bird?

729
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:08,320
How's that possible?

730
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:10,830
It's the 5th day of the month.

731
00:30:10,830 --> 00:30:12,910
It's our market day.

732
00:30:13,110 --> 00:30:15,110
On this day, everyone gathers together

733
00:30:15,110 --> 00:30:16,390
to hold a trading fair

734
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:19,390
and pray for a prosperous life.

735
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:21,480
These people

736
00:30:21,830 --> 00:30:24,520
look just like ordinary folks.

737
00:30:25,790 --> 00:30:27,800
They're all driven by their livelihoods.

738
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:32,280
You seem pretty wealthy.

739
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:34,630
Why not support their businesses?

740
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:35,880
- It's very cheap.
- He's rich.

741
00:30:35,880 --> 00:30:37,480
We'll have this, Master.

742
00:30:37,480 --> 00:30:38,720
Okay, we'll take that.

743
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:40,180
(Peace and Harvest)

744
00:30:44,920 --> 00:30:46,310
Please take a look.

745
00:30:46,310 --> 00:30:47,880
- It's sturdy.
- Forget it.

746
00:30:52,380 --> 00:30:55,940
