Leader,

748
00:30:58,790 --> 00:31:00,150
time spares no one.

749
00:31:00,550 --> 00:31:01,800
You're really old.

750
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:02,840
Liu Guang,

751
00:31:04,790 --> 00:31:07,320
it's been ages since we met in dreams.

752
00:31:07,590 --> 00:31:09,520
You really haven't changed at all.

753
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,670
Leader,

754
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:11,910
