755
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,600
No.

756
00:31:14,030 --> 00:31:16,670
I haven't seen you for a long time.

757
00:31:17,070 --> 00:31:19,150
Stay and chat with me a bit longer.

758
00:31:19,440 --> 00:31:20,670
We're running out of time.

759
00:31:21,240 --> 00:31:23,910
The Martial Artists Association
wants to eliminate us.

760
00:31:24,350 --> 00:31:25,480
Do you have a solution?

761
00:31:25,790 --> 00:31:27,200
Are you really putting all our hopes

762
00:31:27,200 --> 00:31:29,350
on that brat Gou Lingfeng?

763
00:31:31,310 --> 00:31:32,870
Echo From Afar?

764
00:31:33,070 --> 00:31:33,990
Liu Guang.

765
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,640
Liu Guang,

766
00:31:36,200 --> 00:31:37,320
are you still alive?

767
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:39,560
Where the hell

768
00:31:39,750 --> 00:31:41,390
have you been all these years?

769
00:31:42,550 --> 00:31:43,560
Leader,

770
00:31:43,830 --> 00:31:45,080
it's a long story.

771
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:47,110
Without a leader, the divine sect

772
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:48,590
is on the brink of collapse.

773
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:50,560
We don't have time.

774
00:31:51,790 --> 00:31:52,870
I got it.

775
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:56,630
I'll make sure
he takes over the sect soon.

776
00:31:59,030 --> 00:31:59,950
Liu Guang!

777
00:32:00,070 --> 00:32:00,990
Liu Guang!

778
00:32:01,310 --> 00:32:02,230
Liu Guang!

779
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:03,800
Have you left?

780
